### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → ABUSE FLAGS — /api/v1/admin/abuse
### ============================================================================

### List abuse flags
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/abuse?resolved=false
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Resolve abuse flag
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/abuse/{{abuseFlagId}}/resolve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
